lead_paragraph: Canadian rookie Mackenzie Hughes rolled in an 18-foot par putt on the third playoff hole to win the RSM Classic in Georgia on Monday and bring the PGA Tour's final regular tournament of 2016 to a dramatic close.

headline.print_headline: Canadian Rookie Hughes Wins RSM Classic in Playoff
